title: Zac Amico: Strict Parent Trash
description:
Zac Amico joins Kippy and Foley this week for WILD round of Are You Garbage. Zac talks about his insanely strict parents, 2nd marriages, sneaking snacks, and living in a funeral home. You know Zac from the Real Ass Podcast.
